00e9lula vazia,  </li>\n<li><code>1</code> representa uma laranja fresca,  </li>\n<li><code>2</code> representa uma laranja podre.  </li>\n</ul>\n<p>A cada minuto, qualquer laranja fresca que esteja <strong>adjacente em 4 dire\u00e7\u00f5es</strong> (cima, baixo, esquerda, direita) a uma laranja podre se torna podre.  </p>\n<p>Retorne o n\u00famero m\u00ednimo de minutos necess\u00e1rios at\u00e9 que <strong>nenhuma c\u00e9lula contenha uma laranja fresca</strong>.<br />\nSe isso for imposs\u00edvel, retorne <code>-1</code>.</p>\n<p>Segue uma representa\u00e7\u00e3o visual do teste 1.\n<img alt=\"_\" src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/qxcodeed/arcade/master/base/rotten/image.png\" /></p>\n<h2>Submission</h2>\n<p>Aqui, copiamos apenas alguns casos de teste do problema original, ao final, submeta seu c\u00f3digo no LeetCode <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/rotting-oranges/\">nesse link</a>.</p>\n<h2>Tests</h2>\n<div class=\"language-text highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; INSERT Teste 1\n3 3\n2 1 1\n1 1 0\n0 1 1\n======== EXPECT\n4\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; FINISH\n\n\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; INSERT Teste 2\n3 3\n2 1 1\n0 1 1\n1 0 1\n======== EXPECT\n-1\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; FINISH\n\n\n&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; INSERT Teste 3\n1 2\n0 2\n======== EXPECT\n0\n&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt; FINISH\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2>Constraints</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>m == grid.length</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>n == grid[i].length</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>1 &lt;= m, n &lt;= 10</code></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>grid[i][j] \u00e9 0, 1 ou 2.</code></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
